data.description: Come check out this four bedroom rancher that sits on just over half an acre. The home has a split floor plan with the living room and eat in kitchen in the heart of the home. The whole home has laminate flooring except the bathrooms which have tile. The living room has a beautiful barn wood accent wall. All of the kitchen appliances stay with the home. Outside you will find a fully fenced and cross fenced yard. The designated garden area is ready for a new green thumb. There are two chicken coops that are completely enclosed to keep predators out. The 20 x 10 loafing shed can provide shelter to your critters and also has a tack room attached. There is a round pen already in place for the horse enthusiasts. The oversized garage is 28 x 22, leaving plenty of room for cars, tools and toys. The home has easy access to Highway 115 and is only about 30 minutes to Colorado Springs or Pueblo.
